name: LibraryPlaylists.Relationships
desc: The relationships for a library playlist resource.

items.name: catalog
items.desc: The corresponding playlist in the Apple Music catalog the playlist is associated with.Fetch limits: None (associated with at most one catalog playlist).

items.name: tracks
items.desc: The library songs and library music videos included in the playlist. By default, tracks not included. Only available when fetching a single library playlist resource by ID. Fetch limits: 100 default, 100 maximum.
